{
  "stem": "21788.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They put a down payment on a truck and a trailer, outfitted it like a dental and a physician's practice, and also pulled a trailer as living quarters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The physician got cold feet, dropped out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father lost whatever he put down on that particular venture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He kept trying to get out of Germany several times, any country that would take him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The unfortunate thing was that at that time, doors of other countries began to close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The quotas, which were quite generous at one time, began to drop drastically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] You just could not get any permission to go into these countries, be they England, be they United States, be they Australia, be they anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It became harder and harder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "On top of that, then there was a black market building up of trying to get visas, permission, exit visas, entrance visas, all those things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it turned out to be bogus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My father again got some bogus visas which then were not accepted, lost more money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all between 1931, '32, clear into 1938, when we finally got permission, with a ridiculously low price, five US dollars at the time, to come to Shanghai, China, Shanghai, China, the part that was occupied by the Japanese government.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's name was Else, E-L-S-E, again Palnitzky, married my father, Chaim, 'khime.'",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both my parents were from Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they got married in Berlin in 1927.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, I came along in 1928.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I do have a sister too, by the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came along in 1930, two years younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her name is Evelyne, E-V-E-L-Y-N-E, Evelyne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother was kind of a socialite, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
